You have a running container named my_app, but it's not behaving as expected. You want to check its logs to debug any errors.
Write the command to view its logs and follow new logentries in real-time.

step1:- make sure that my_app should be running 
  docker ps
step2:- To check its logs
  docker logs my_app
step3:- For new logentries in real-time
  docker logs -f my_app
